        "subject": "LU-4557 ldiskfs: pre-mount/umount ldiskfs to fix inconsistency",
        "message": "LU-4557 ldiskfs: pre-mount/umount ldiskfs to fix inconsistency\n\nIf OSS crashes when there is active I/O, the free block/inode number\nin super block will be false. That will cause inconsistency of ldiskfs\nafter OSS service is up. This patch fixes this problem by pre-mount/\numount ldiskfs.\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I68effb0851cb5aa9582e0d94652c759754b5aac4\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
